Package com.mycompany.assignment

Class Subscription

java.lang.Object
com.mycompany.assignment.Subscription
public final class Subscription extends Object
Represents a subscription associated with a paying customer. This class calculates the total cost of magazines and supplements for the subscription and provides methods to retrieve and set subscription details.
